OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1772885582
OL,3,CEvent at Parliament aims to attract
OL,4,Cinvestment and boost growth in Cumbria
OL,6,FA gathering of investors, industry
OL,7,Frepresentatives and political leaders
OL,8,Fwill take place in the House of
OL,9,FParliament to attract investment into
OL,10,FCumbria and encourage economic growth
OL,11,Fin the county.
OL,13,FThe 'Cumbria Day' event will be hosted
OL,14,Fby Workington and Whitehaven's MP,
OL,15,FJosh MacAlister OBE, with Enterprising
OL,16,FCumbria delivering the event.
OL,18,FRepresentatives from Cumberland
OL,19,FCouncil, Westmorland and Furness
OL,20,FCouncil and the new Cumbria Combined
OL,21,FAuthority will also be in attendance.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
