CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1772885582
OL,3,CEvent at Parliament aims to attract
OL,4,Cinvestment and boost growth in Cumbria
OL,6,FThe event aims to promote the 'Cumbria
OL,7,FGoing for Growth Strategy', and
OL,8,Fshowcase the possibilities for
OL,9,Finvestment and business partnerships
OL,10,Fin the county.
OL,12,FDavid Beeby, Chair of Enterprising
OL,13,FCumbria, said: "Cumbria Day in
OL,14,FWestminster gives us a powerful
OL,15,Fplatform to share the ambition set out
OL,16,Fin our Going for Growth strategy - a
OL,17,Fclear, long-term vision for
OL,18,Fsustainable, inclusive prosperity that
OL,19,Fharnesses the county's world-leading
OL,20,Fstrengths."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1772885582
OL,3,CEvent at Parliament aims to attract
OL,4,Cinvestment and boost growth in Cumbria
OL,6,FSome of the sectors set to be
OL,7,Fhighlighted at the event include
OL,8,Fdefence, advanced manufacturing, the
OL,9,Fvisitor economy and natural assets,
OL,10,Fand transport and infrastructure.
OL,12,FKey Cumbrian businesses and
OL,13,Forganisations will demonstrate the
OL,14,Frange and scale of opportunities in
OL,15,FCumbria at the event, which Mr Beeby
OL,16,Fdescribed as "a call to action".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
