PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1772885582
OL,3,CEvent at Parliament aims to attract
OL,4,Cinvestment and boost growth in Cumbria
OL,6,FJosh MacAllister MP said: "Cumbria has
OL,7,Falways played a vital role in our
OL,8,Fnational story - from defence and
OL,9,Fadvanced manufacturing to clean energy
OL,10,Fand food production - and we are ready
OL,11,Fto build on that legacy.
OL,13,F"Cumbria Day in Westminster is about
OL,14,Fdemonstrating that ours is not a
OL,15,Fperipheral economy, but a nationally
OL,16,Fsignificant one. By bringing together
OL,17,Finvestors, policymakers and business
OL,18,Fleaders, we are sending a clear
OL,19,Fmessage: Cumbria is ambitious, co-
OL,20,Fordinated and open for investment."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
