PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1772885582
OL,3,CEvent at Parliament aims to attract
OL,4,Cinvestment and boost growth in Cumbria
OL,6,FJohn Barradell OBE, Interim Chief
OL,7,FExecutive of the Cumbria Combined
OL,8,FAuthority, added: "We're already
OL,9,Fleading in areas like clean energy,
OL,10,Fadvanced manufacturing and defence,
OL,11,Fand there's real global interest in
OL,12,Fthe work happening here.
OL,14,F"Cumbria Day in Westminster is our
OL,15,Fchance to show that we're serious
OL,16,Fabout growth, serious about
OL,17,Fpartnership and ready to step onto the
OL,18,Finternational stage with confidence.
OL,19,FThis is about backing our people, our
OL,20,Fplaces and our potential."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
